data.title: Oando plc annual report 2015
data.meta_description: Oando plc annual report 2015 - Download as a PDF or view online for free
data.text: This document is the 2015 annual report and accounts of Oando PLC, an integrated energy solutions group in sub-Saharan Africa. It summarizes that 2015 was a challenging year for Oando due to declining global oil prices and economic turbulence in Nigeria. However, Oando executed on its strategic plan by growing its upstream assets, divesting parts of its downstream business, continuing expansion of its gas and power business, and divesting its oil field services business to focus on deleveraging. While low oil prices are expected to continue into 2016, Oando remains committed to transforming Nigeria's energy sector.
